claim: WWI was fought from the 28th of July, 1914 to the 11th of November, 1918.
premise_source_doc_sentence: World War I  (  WWI or WW1  )  , also known as the First World War , the Great War , or the War to End All Wars , was a global war originating in Europe that lasted from 28 July 1914 to 11 November 1918 .
